        <fileDesc>
            <titleStmt>
                <title>Translation of 太平經 into (English)</title>
                <editor role="translator">Barbara Hendrischke</editor>
            </titleStmt>
            <publicationStmt>
                <p>published electronically as part of the TLS project at https://hxwd.org<seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.2783" xml:lang="en" resp="#barbara.hendrischke" modified="2020-05-03T09:23:04.354+09:00"/>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.2797" xml:lang="en" resp="#barbara.hendrischke" modified="2020-05-03T09:22:36.044+09:00">What are the crimes that all regular people commit?</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.2798" xml:lang="en" resp="#barbara.hendrischke" modified="2020-05-03T09:25:54.132+09:00">A regular person does nothing wrong.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.2799" xml:lang="en" resp="#barbara.hendrischke" modified="2020-05-03T09:25:16.936+09:00">What crimes should he commit?</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.2796" xml:lang="en" resp="#barbara.hendrischke" modified="2020-05-03T09:26:23.326+09:00">Step forward, Perfected.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.2800" xml:lang="en" resp="#barbara.hendrischke" modified="2020-05-03T09:27:01.41+09:00">Oh,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.2801" xml:lang="en" resp="#barbara.hendrischke" modified="2020-05-03T09:27:46.161+09:00">How can you be so dumb!</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.2802" xml:lang="en" resp="#barbara.hendrischke" modified="2020-05-03T09:28:56.171+09:00">Foolish as I am I have not even started to comprehend. </seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.2803" xml:lang="en" resp="#barbara.hendrischke" modified="2020-05-03T09:30:21.353+09:00">Never in my life have I heard </seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.2804" xml:lang="en" resp="#barbara.hendrischke" modified="2020-05-03T09:31:57.863+09:00">that someone has committed a crime who has done nothing wrong and not broken the law. </seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.2805" xml:lang="en" resp="#barbara.hendrischke" modified="2020-05-03T09:32:45.215+09:00">If this is what you are saying </seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.2806" xml:lang="en" resp="#barbara.hendrischke" modified="2020-05-03T09:34:17.732+09:00">you state what is commonly said. </seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.2807" xml:lang="en" resp="#barbara.hendrischke" modified="2020-05-03T09:36:43.049+09:00">You do not realise that people in general commit, in fact,  six big crimes</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.2808" xml:lang="en" resp="#barbara.hendrischke" modified="2020-05-03T09:37:17.698+09:00">that are unforgivable. </seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.2809" xml:lang="en" resp="#barbara.hendrischke" modified="2020-05-03T09:37:44.275+09:00">They are put on trial in person</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.2810" xml:lang="en" resp="#barbara.hendrischke" modified="2020-05-04T16:35:17.699+09:00">or have their progeny dragged in</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.2811" xml:lang="en" resp="#barbara.hendrischke" modified="2020-05-04T16:36:25.206+09:00">You, Perfected, have studied</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.2812" xml:lang="en" resp="#barbara.hendrischke" modified="2020-05-03T09:45:11.188+09:00">but are not aware of these obvious crimes.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.2813" xml:lang="en" resp="#barbara.hendrischke" modified="2020-05-04T16:37:05.044+09:00">Although you have studied you are not enraged by [the people's] distraction?"</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.2814" xml:lang="en" resp="#barbara.hendrischke" modified="2020-05-04T16:37:53.672+09:00">"Foolish as I am I don't care. </seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.2816" xml:lang="en" resp="#barbara.hendrischke" modified="2020-05-04T16:38:46.273+09:00">"You may not care,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.2817" xml:lang="en" resp="#barbara.hendrischke" modified="2020-05-04T16:39:37.748+09:00">but we all know that when common people die they are afflicted by resentment. </seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.2818" xml:lang="en" resp="#barbara.hendrischke" modified="2020-05-03T10:00:27.609+09:00">They truly come to their end from being without understanding. </seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.2819" xml:lang="en" resp="#barbara.hendrischke" modified="2020-05-03T10:02:04.858+09:00">What the situation is they realise only the moment they die.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.2820" xml:lang="en" resp="#barbara.hendrischke" modified="2020-05-03T10:02:42.933+09:00">Since the division between heaven and earth</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.2821" xml:lang="en" resp="#barbara.hendrischke" modified="2020-05-03T10:04:12.483+09:00">the people in general have been blind until someone has enlightened them. </seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.2823" xml:lang="en" resp="#barbara.hendrischke" modified="2020-05-03T10:05:16.494+09:00">I would like to hear what it was. </seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.2824" xml:lang="en" resp="#barbara.hendrischke" modified="2020-05-04T16:16:02.69+09:00">Well, </seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.2825" xml:lang="en" resp="#barbara.hendrischke" modified="2020-05-04T16:19:01.621+09:00">To accumulate teachings without end </seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.2826" xml:lang="en" resp="#barbara.hendrischke" modified="2020-05-04T16:20:15.045+09:00">but refuse to instruct others on how to dissolve such blindness and search for life </seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.2827" xml:lang="en" resp="#barbara.hendrischke" modified="2020-05-04T16:21:04.911+09:00">is an unforgivable crime. </seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.2828" xml:lang="en" resp="#barbara.hendrischke" modified="2020-05-04T16:21:17.324+09:00">The culprit is tried in person</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.2829" xml:lang="en" resp="#barbara.hendrischke" modified="2020-05-04T16:21:31.975+09:00">or has his progeny dragged in.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.2830" xml:lang="en" resp="#barbara.hendrischke" modified="2020-05-04T16:22:17.674+09:00">This is so</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.2831" xml:lang="en" resp="#barbara.hendrischke" modified="2020-05-04T16:24:11.754+09:00">because he destructs what heaven has taught </seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.2832" xml:lang="en" resp="#barbara.hendrischke" modified="2020-05-04T16:24:53.842+09:00">and heaven is resentful.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.2833" xml:lang="en" resp="#barbara.hendrischke" modified="2020-05-04T16:25:53.205+09:00">To amass virtue without end</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.2834" xml:lang="en" resp="#barbara.hendrischke" modified="2020-05-04T16:32:00.608+09:00">but refuse to  instruct others on  how to pay attention to preserving virtue </seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.2835" xml:lang="en" resp="#barbara.hendrischke" modified="2020-05-04T16:30:29.084+09:00">and nourishing one's disposition</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.2836" xml:lang="en" resp="#barbara.hendrischke" modified="2020-05-04T16:33:58.268+09:00">is an unforgivable crime. </seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.2837" xml:lang="en" resp="#barbara.hendrischke" modified="2020-05-04T16:34:12.46+09:00">The culprit is tried in person </seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.2838" xml:lang="en" resp="#barbara.hendrischke" modified="2020-05-04T16:34:28.771+09:00">or has his progeny dragged in. </seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.2815" xml:lang="en" resp="#barbara.hendrischke" modified="2020-05-04T16:38:22.511+09:00">I am not enraged." </seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.2839" xml:lang="en" resp="#barbara.hendrischke" modified="2020-05-04T16:40:01.85+09:00">This is so</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.2840" xml:lang="en" resp="#barbara.hendrischke" modified="2020-05-04T16:41:15.123+09:00">because he destroys the virtue that earth has nourished</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.2841" xml:lang="en" resp="#barbara.hendrischke" modified="2020-05-04T16:41:51.461+09:00">and earth is resentful. </seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.2842" xml:lang="en" resp="#barbara.hendrischke" modified="2020-05-04T16:42:40.494+09:00">He is severely condemned.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.2843" xml:lang="en" resp="#barbara.hendrischke" modified="2020-05-04T16:43:47.526+09:00">Another person may pile up goods, millions and millions</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.2844" xml:lang="en" resp="#barbara.hendrischke" modified="2020-05-04T16:44:45.686+09:00">but refuse to save people who are desperate and rescue those in need. </seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.2845" xml:lang="en" resp="#barbara.hendrischke" modified="2020-05-04T16:46:19.711+09:00">To let others die from hunger and cold </seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.2846" xml:lang="en" resp="#barbara.hendrischke" modified="2020-05-04T16:46:45.265+09:00">is and unforgivable crime.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.2847" xml:lang="en" resp="#barbara.hendrischke" modified="2020-05-04T16:47:04.454+09:00">The culprit is tried in person </seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.2848" xml:lang="en" resp="#barbara.hendrischke" modified="2020-05-04T16:47:19.894+09:00">or has his progeny dragged in.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.2849" xml:lang="en" resp="#barbara.hendrischke" modified="2020-05-04T16:47:58.605+09:00">This is so </seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.2850" xml:lang="en" resp="#barbara.hendrischke" modified="2020-05-04T16:49:26.739+09:00">because the products of the harmony [between Yin and Yang] </seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.2851" xml:lang="en" resp="#barbara.hendrischke" modified="2020-05-04T16:50:22.945+09:00">are the means by which heaven and earth show humaneness</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.2852" xml:lang="en" resp="#barbara.hendrischke" modified="2020-05-04T16:51:23.733+09:00">and provide sufficient support for all</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.2853" xml:lang="en" resp="#barbara.hendrischke" modified="2020-05-04T16:52:53.591+09:00">so that people do not become desperate. </seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.2854" xml:lang="en" resp="#barbara.hendrischke" modified="2020-05-04T16:54:21.162+09:00">But someone may interrupt this process by collecting [these products]</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.2855" xml:lang="en" resp="#barbara.hendrischke" modified="2020-05-04T16:54:33.834+09:00">so that they cannot be spread.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.2856" xml:lang="en" resp="#barbara.hendrischke" modified="2020-05-04T16:57:02.448+09:00">This person is an enemy to the harmonious vapour (qi) of heaven and earth. </seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.2857" xml:lang="en" resp="#barbara.hendrischke" modified="2020-05-04T16:57:22.42+09:00">He is tried in person</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.2858" xml:lang="en" resp="#barbara.hendrischke" modified="2020-05-04T16:57:33.771+09:00">or has his progeny dragged in. </seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.2859" xml:lang="en" resp="#barbara.hendrischke" modified="2020-05-04T17:00:20.896+09:00">x會y當 One must not for long [retain] what one has been collecting</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.2860" xml:lang="en" resp="#barbara.hendrischke" modified="2020-05-04T17:00:47.155+09:00">but pass it on.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.2861" xml:lang="en" resp="#barbara.hendrischke" modified="2020-05-04T17:01:15.036+09:00">When heaven brings people to life</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.2862" xml:lang="en" resp="#barbara.hendrischke" modified="2020-05-04T17:02:09.52+09:00">it lets them know</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.2863" xml:lang="en" resp="#barbara.hendrischke" modified="2020-05-04T17:02:39.214+09:00">how to love what is good and detest what is evil.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.2864" xml:lang="en" resp="#barbara.hendrischke" modified="2020-05-04T17:03:35.394+09:00">Someone fortunate enough to have knowledge</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.2865" xml:lang="en" resp="#barbara.hendrischke" modified="2020-05-04T17:04:45.323+09:00">will know of the teachings that origin in heaven but may think them worthless</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.2866" xml:lang="en" resp="#barbara.hendrischke" modified="2020-05-04T17:05:30.349+09:00">and refuse to resolutely study how to save himself. </seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.2867" xml:lang="en" resp="#barbara.hendrischke" modified="2020-05-04T17:06:02.866+09:00">He will perhaps live long</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.2868" xml:lang="en" resp="#barbara.hendrischke" modified="2020-05-04T17:07:13.024+09:00">in the body that heaven's dispensation and the ancestors have bestowed on him</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.2869" xml:lang="en" resp="#barbara.hendrischke" modified="2020-05-04T17:09:04.715+09:00">but will think lightly of himself </seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.2870" xml:lang="en" resp="#barbara.hendrischke" modified="2020-05-04T17:09:43.371+09:00">and refrain from study. He will view death</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.2871" xml:lang="en" resp="#barbara.hendrischke" modified="2020-05-04T17:10:37.408+09:00">in a careless manner. When close to death</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.2872" xml:lang="en" resp="#barbara.hendrischke" modified="2020-05-04T17:10:55.97+09:00">he will turn resentful. </seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.2873" xml:lang="en" resp="#barbara.hendrischke" modified="2020-05-04T17:11:52.642+09:00">[This is] an unforgivable crime. </seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.2874" xml:lang="en" resp="#barbara.hendrischke" modified="2020-05-04T17:12:05.711+09:00">He is put on trial in person</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.2875" xml:lang="en" resp="#barbara.hendrischke" modified="2020-05-04T17:12:14.875+09:00">or has his progeny dragged in.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.2876" xml:lang="en" resp="#barbara.hendrischke" modified="2020-05-04T17:15:23.83+09:00">He makes people live without understanding </seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.2877" xml:lang="en" resp="#barbara.hendrischke" modified="2020-05-04T17:15:30.541+09:00">and be resented by heaven. </seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.2878" xml:lang="en" resp="#barbara.hendrischke" modified="2020-05-04T17:20:06.266+09:00">Since this is so,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.2879" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-05-05T06:45:12.31+09:00">[for天read人] when people resolutely enact Dao</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.2880" xml:lang="en" resp="#barbara.hendrischke" modified="2020-05-04T17:21:06.687+09:00">there is constant good luck</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.2881" xml:lang="en" resp="#barbara.hendrischke" modified="2020-05-04T17:21:53.06+09:00">while there is misfortune and death when Dao is ignored. </seg>
                </p>
